{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The beauty of it was they didn't have to tell me to twice to-- to lie in the snow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I just lied down in the snow, fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the next second-- for a while I could hear-- I mean not the second, but for the next minute I could hear for a minute the machine guns firing, the SS men taking up position with their machine guns.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "A group, [SPEAKING GERMAN]. 20 men attack this forest. 30 men attack that forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You know, the orders went out from the officers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know, and then I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I had a long sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They-- they had a regular battle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They went into the forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The forest people were shooting at us, bullets flying everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then after I don't know how much time, I had a good sound sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But eventually the two Israelis told to me, get up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Get up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They just said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And to my amazement, the pain was completely gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I had one hour of sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It makes a big difference, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I could walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And after [INAUDIBLE], we arrived again to a circus stadium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Same story again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I could get near a building this time where it was in the stands or something where it was a bit of a cover from the-- so 10 people close together.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was kind of warmed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The next day, the next morning-- so I survived this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This was the nearest I came, apart from the selection on the 1st of October, which was a very close shave, of course.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But this was a sure thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
